comments: I was only really able to learn the broad terms of the shapes in the time and examples given. I wasn't able to pick up on any intricacies of how the spellings varied or were adapted. I don't know if they were because of the colour but I wasn't able to pick up on any patterns like that to work out if there was a rule and what it was. I found learning the general terms for the shapes easy but that was it. I would have like to have learnt about the more intricate spellings according to the colour and/or shape but I wasn't able to.
